"you will need to set the link:{hibernate-orm-docs-url}#database-dialect[Hibernate ORM dialect] explicitly:"
msgstr "如果 xref:datasource.adoc#other-databases[您的数据库没有相应的 Quarkus 扩展，] 或者由于某种原因默认设置不符合您的需求，则需要显式设置 link:{hibernate-orm-docs-url}#database-dialect[Hibernate ORM 方言] ："

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/3.8/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`{config-file}` with an explicit `dialect`"
msgstr "包含显式 `方言` 的 `{config-file}`"

#. type: Plain text
